# Types of Arguments

## 1. Positional Arguments

Arguments are passed in order.

```python
def add(a, b):
    print(a + b)

add(10, 20)
```

Output

```
30
```

---

## 2. Keyword Arguments

```python
def student(name, age):
    print(name, age)

student(age=20, name="Rahul")
```

Output

```
Rahul 20
```

---

## 3. Default Arguments

```python
def greet(name="Guest"):
    print(name)

greet()

greet("Rahul")
```

Output

```
Guest
Rahul
```

