# Local Variables

Variables created inside a function.

```python
def demo():
    x = 10
    print(x)

demo()
```

Output

```
10
```

Outside the function

```python
print(x)
```

Error

```
NameError
```

---

# Global Variables

Variables created outside functions.

```python
name = "Rahul"

def show():
    print(name)

show()
```

Output

```
Rahul
```

---

# Local vs Global

| Local | Global |
|--------|---------|
| Inside Function | Outside Function |
| Limited Scope | Available Everywhere |
| Temporary | Exists Until Program Ends |

