# Common Mistakes

## Forgetting Parentheses

Wrong

```python
greet
```

Correct

```python
greet()
```

---

## Forgetting return

```python
def add(a,b):
    a+b
```

Correct

```python
return a+b
```

---

## Wrong Number of Arguments

```python
def add(a,b):
    return a+b

add(10)
```

Error

```
TypeError
```

